                     <interp inst="t18210606-112-person1265" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            ; the prisoner came to the house to see his master. I missed a table-spoon the evening before.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I beg for mercy.</p>
